erty sources, or built-in Java properties parsing without Docker, extra dependencies, or required environment.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No required setup. Keep tests focused on hoplite-core APIs such as ConfigLoaderBuilder, MapPropertySource, SystemPropertiesPropertySource, EnvironmentVariablesPropertySource, built-in .properties parsing, decoders, preprocessors, and resource loading. If tests intentionally use YAML, JSON, TOML, or HOCON files, those formats require separate Hoplite modules, but that is optional integration coverage rather than required setup for hoplite-core.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Hoplite documentation commonly demonstrates YAML/JSON-style configuration; generated tests that copy those examples without adding the matching hoplite-yaml, hoplite-json, hoplite-toml, or hoplite-hocon module would fail with parser/format errors.\",\n    \"The 3.0.0.RC1 artifact uses Kotlin 2.1.0 runtime artifacts transitively; native-image failures may still require metadata changes rather than workflow setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08244e9c4c856dcd016a42221a493881968a44108aad78c3be\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 523, "output": 801, "cacheRead": 44544, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 45868, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782718992206, "responseId": "resp_08244e9c4c856dcd016a422210f0308196aabef99d51e9bb72"}}
